Spreadtrum Communications Denies Muddy Waters Allegations on Accounting

-- B y   M a r k   L e e
-- 
2011-06-29T03:49:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/spreadtrum-denies-muddy-waters-allegations-it-may-have-misstated-finances.html
Spreadtrum Communications Inc. (SPRD) , the
latest Chinese company questioned by short-seller Muddy Waters
LLC over its accounting, denied allegations the Chinese chip
designer may have misstated financial results.  “Their questions do not have any basis,” Shannon Gao,
chief financial officer at Shanghai-based Spreadtrum, said in a
phone interview today. Spreadtrum’s auditor,
PricewaterhouseCoopers, “showed strong support for us,” Gao
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
